  "title": "Banking: Deputy Finance Head/Finance Manager (Financial, Regulatory and Tax)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>*Seeking for a Deputy Finance Head/Finance Manager has minimum of 7 years’ banking experience handling Financial and Regulatory reporting and Tax*</strong></em><br /></p><p><strong>THE COMPANY</strong></p><p>This bank has a solid foundation. With their strong financials and leadership, they seek to grow their business and bring it to greater heights. Currently, they seek for a Deputy Head/Finance Manager to be part of their Finance team.</p><p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare/review Financial and Statutory Accounting</li><li>Review MAS/Regulatory reporting</li><li>Ensure accurate FATCA/CRS and Corporate tax</li><li>Dealing with budgeting/financial analysis</li><li>Any adhoc IT systems projects/enhancements</li><li>Collaborate effectively with other internal and external stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Accountancy/Commerce or ACCA or any other relevant education</li><li>Minimum 7 years of banking experience handling Financial and Regulatory reporting and Tax</li><li>Independent, attentive to details, strong interpersonal and communication skills</li></ul><p>If you will like to explore this opportunity, please email your resume in Microsoft Word format to marie@resolutehunter.com</p><p>We thank you for your interest and will contact shortlisted candidates for more detailed discussion.</p><p>For more job openings, please visit our website at https://resolutehunter.com/opportunities/<br /></p><p>EA Licence 18C9105</p><p>EA Reg R1105305</p>",
